15. Nicole Rehema (DC Bweremana RDC);
16. Eugenie Kanengele (FCF Lupopo RDC)
Attaquantes :
17. Déborah Ngalula (La Roche Vendee / D2 France) ;
18. Esther Dikishasha (FCF Mazembe RDC);
